# ============================================
# COMMON ERRORS & SOLUTIONS
# ============================================

# ERROR: "Insufficient surplus"
# SOLUTION: Submit more energy data with production > consumption

# ERROR: "Insufficient tokens"
# SOLUTION: Energy tokens are minted when surplus is registered
#           Check /api/energy/user/:address to see token balance

# ERROR: "Insufficient allowance"
# SOLUTION: Call /api/marketplace/approve-marketplace first

# ERROR: "Update too frequent" (Price Oracle)
# SOLUTION: Wait for minUpdateInterval (default 5 minutes)
#           OR call contract setMinUpdateInterval(60) for testing

# ERROR: "Listing is not active"
# SOLUTION: Check /api/marketplace/listings to see active listings

# ERROR: "Cannot buy your own listing"
# SOLUTION: Use different address for buyer and seller

# ERROR: "Insufficient energy in listing"
# SOLUTION: Check listing.remainingAmount before buying

# ============================================
# SUCCESS INDICATORS
# ============================================
# ✅ User registered successfully
# ✅ Energy data submitted (surplus > 0)
# ✅ Tokens minted for surplus producers
# ✅ Marketplace approved to spend tokens
# ✅ Energy listed successfully
# ✅ Energy purchased successfully
# ✅ Tokens transferred buyer → seller
# ✅ Payment transferred (ETH)
# ✅ Trade history updated
# ============================================